a-days are bogged down by serious kaarmic blockages that require a lot of effort to overcome.\n \nOf course, if a superman is available to you to help, he may push the boulder in a second. But there are hardly any supermen anymore.\n \nIn the old days, many priests existed who did intense sadhana, became enlightened and were like walking fire. Also, many temples existed, where such priests, great yogis and rishis did sadhana and left great energy. Thus, big kaarmik problems could also be solved with one pooja, one homam, one abhishekam, one visit to a temple etc.\n \nSuch priests and temples are quite rare today. Do not expect one pooja, one archana, one homam or one abhishekam to solve problems.\n \nHowever, little bit at a time adds up over time. If you keep doing sadhana (pooja, archana, homam, abhishekam etc) regularly, it will slowly add up.\n \nBest regards,\nNarasimha\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\n  Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,\n&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:\n                  http://www.VedicAstrologer.org\n     Films that make a difference: http://SaraswatiFilms.org\n     Spirituality: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom\n  Jyotish writings: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\n \n---- Harish Mohanbabu &lt;harishm_26@...&gt; wrote: \n&gt; \n&gt; || Jai Gurudev ||\n&gt; Namaste Narasimha,\n&gt; &gt;&gt;The catch is this: Doing a one-off homam (or any ritual) once every 6 months or so is unlikely to cause any considerable material or spiritual benefit. \n&gt; I wanted to ask this for quite some time now.  When you say any ritual, do you also mean rituals like archana and abhishegams that are performed in temples?  \n&gt; Kindly clarify.\n&gt; Sincerely,\n&gt; Harish\n&gt; \n&gt;       Namaste,\n&gt; \n&gt; &gt; I would still go to a priest for doing homam.