ceed over time.\n&gt; \n&gt; *        *        *\n&gt; \n&gt; Jyotisha readings that you talk about the end are a different ball game. They are mostly an intellectual exercise and can be done well by one without spiritual energy. But, doing a ritual for someone and giving a boost to one&#39;s material and spiritual pursuits (using one&#39;s own spiritual energy by using the ritual as a tool) is a spiritual exercise and one without a good level of spiritual energy cannot do it well. These days, people hardly have enough spiritual energy to fix their own blockages and how can they take care of others?\n&gt; \n&gt; *        *        *\n&gt; \n&gt; &gt; I apologize if I offended you. I&#39;m a nobody compared to you.\n&gt; \n&gt; No offense taken. Whose caliber is what and whose potential is what, only god knows!\n&gt; \n&gt; Best regards,\n&gt; Narasimha\n\n\n"}}